{"name":"Misfortune","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Twisting fate, the psyker focuses his inner eye to ensure that his foe suffers every possible calamity that ill-fortune could provide. From embarrassing mishaps to life-and-death struggles, chance itself betrays the target at every turn.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Inflict bad luck  on target","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 45","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"20*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker nominates a single target in range and line of sight who opposes this power with a Willpower test. If the target fails to resist the power, misfortune follows it wherever it goes. For the duration of this power, the target&rsquo;s Armour points are reduced in all locations by half the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating, rounded up. The target&rsquo;s weapons also jam on any attack in which they fail to hit their target.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"5eNyMEx158Oit5eU"}
{"name":"Scrier's Gaze","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The most accomplished diviners are not only able to see into the future, but also the present. Unbound by the limits of mere physical vision, his mind peers far and wide, with little able to hide from his sight.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"See events elsewhere","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psyniscience rank 2","action":"Special","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":""},"range":"Self","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>To begin the ritual, the psyker must spend at least thirty minutes using assorted psychic foci to concentrate his vision&mdash; drawing Tarot cards, casting runes, gazing deep into fire, or other methods as varied as the stars of the Imperium. At the end of this time, he makes his Focus Power test to project his vision over the area, with the GM revealing information based on the degrees of success, as described on Table 6&ndash;4: Scrier&rsquo;s Gaze Results.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6pyu3n7ED2QIorNR"}
{"name":"Precognition","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>In one of the most viscerally intense applications of the Divination discipline, the psyker witnesses solid and perfectly lifelike visions of his own future. Peering into moments yet to come, he can use this information to ensure or avoid future fates.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Gain re-rolls","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Perception 45, Willpower 45","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":-20,"test":"Psyniscience"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker gains a number of re-rolls equal to his psy rating that last until the beginning of the his next turn. For the duration of that round, whenever the psyker or an ally in range makes a test or damage roll, the psyker may spend one of the rerolls to allow that ally to re-roll all dice involved in the roll. If the psyker is killed or rendered Unconscious before the beginning of his next turn, all remaining re-rolls are lost.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"9ZEWcnbrLrDTd2w9"}
{"name":"Forewarning","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Foreseeing his foes&rsquo; intentions, the psyker taps into the Warp and, like dropping a small pebble into a pool, sends ripples to slightly shift the course of events. Without moving a muscle, the psyker saves his ally from certain injury and leaves his enemy baffled.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Foresee and prevent attack on allies","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Perception 50","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Psyniscience"},"range":"3*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>For the duration of this power, a number of allies within range equal to the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating, plus the psyker himself, gain a bonus to all Evasion tests equal to twice the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating. Allies affected by this power lose its benefits as soon as they move out of range.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"EYphfnkc7t6fJCAA"}
{"name":"Perfect Timing","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>So accurate are the diviner&rsquo;s premonitions, that he can predict the exact moment his foe will expose himself as a target. Further, the psyker can forge a link with his allies, momentarily intertwining their fortunes, so that they might fire in perfect unison, already squeezing their weapons&rsquo; triggers before the foe is aware.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Allow self and allies to ignore cover whenshooting","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Perception 55","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Psyniscience"},"range":"3*PR","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>For the duration of this power, the psyker and a number of allies equal to his psy rating within range, ignore the effects of cover when firing on a target. If their attacks would strike a Hit Location on the enemy that would benefit from cover, that benefit is ignored. Allies affected by this power lose its benefits as soon as they move out of range.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"XbEp1XyWEANv4g9I"}
{"name":"Winding Fate","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>By touching a character or item, the psyker sees visions into that subject&rsquo;s future and past. Though ghostly and laced with tendrils of Warp-smoke, these images reveal not only what was, but what is yet to be.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"See targetâ€™s past  or future","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Perception 50","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Psyniscience"},"range":"Self","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The vision lasts for a number of seconds equal to the twice the psy rating, and can be from the subject&rsquo;s future or past a number of days equal to the psy rating. The higher the psy rating, the more the psyker can control what his flashes focus on (at the GM&rsquo;s discretion).</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"iLNHgszXAeTwsbuM"}
{"name":"Foreboding","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker gains an unnatural sixth sense. With this inexplicable insight, he knows how and where his enemies will attack, dodging blows and lasblasts with contemptuous and frightening ease.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Foresee and prevent incoming attacks","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psyniscience rank 1","action":"Reaction","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Perception"},"range":"Self","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>In any situation where the psyker would be called upon to make an Evasion test, he may instead attempt to use this power. If the power is successful, the psyker avoids the attack exactly as if he has passed an Evasion test with the number of degrees of success he scored on the Focus Power test.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"mHnx1HfGW26t0lOZ"}
{"name":"Prescience","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker sees brief, fuzzy flashes into his immediate future, which he can use to guide the warband&rsquo;s aim against their enemies. Though the glimpses are short, such foretelling can mean the difference between life and death when in combat.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Gain bonuses in  combat skills","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psyniscience Rank 1","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Psyniscience"},"range":"3*PR","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>For the duration of this power, the psyker and a number of allies equal to his psy rating within range, gain a bonus to their Weapon Skill and Ballistic Skill tests equal to twice the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating. Allies affected by this power lose its benefit as soon as they move out of range.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"qZIoYRFCpOXRniFu"}
{"name":"Warp Perception","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker opens his senses to the Warp, allowing unnatural tendrils of energy to augment his own perceptions. His flesh no longer limited, he casts his gaze wider and hungrily scents prey from farther afield.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Gain Unnatural Senses trait","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 35","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Psyniscience"},"range":"Self","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker gains the Unnatural Senses (X) trait, where the X value is equal to the psy rating multiplied by 10.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/third-eye.svg","effects":[],"_id":"qh1qt3NfBYmYEu18"}
